## FlakeDrop Community Edition

This license applies to the FlakeDrop Community Edition, which includes:

- Command-line interface (CLI)
- Core deployment functionality
- Git repository integration
- Basic rollback capabilities
- Schema comparison tools
- Standard security features

For enterprise features such as web GUI, advanced security, SSO integration, 
and commercial support, please see FlakeDrop Enterprise Edition.

